Package: UXtoolbox
Title: A Comprehensive UX & Human Factors Research Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohsen", "Rafiei", , "moo.rafiei@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5136-1733"))
Description: UXtoolbox provides powerful tools for user experience (UX) and human factors (HF) research. 
    It includes statistical tests, predictive models, bootstrapping techniques, and visualization functions 
    to support data analysis in usability testing, A/B testing, and cognitive load assessment.
